	<description>
	Slug Slasher is a 2D action platformer where the player takes on the role of a chef who must defend the world from an onslaught of giant slugs with only his trusty bucket of salt. 
	</description>
	
	<history>
	Slug Slasher started out as a project within Indiana University's Hoosier Games game development club. Development has continued for about a year and is due to finish during the summer of 2018.
	</history>

	<features>
		<feature>Over-the-top visuals, sounds, and situations</feature>
		<feature>Punchy, satisfying combat</feature>
		<feature>Classic platformer beat-em-up level and enemy design</feature>
